<script type="text/javascript">
function togPhase(n) {
	var e = document.getElementById('phasehint' + n);
	e.style.display = e.style.display == 'none' ? 'block' : 'none';
}
function togAllPhases(display) {
	for (var i = 1; i <= 50; i++) {
		var e = document.getElementById('phasehint' + i);
		if (!e) break;
		e.style.display = display;
	}
}
function addHint(n) {
	var e = document.getElementById('phase');
	for (var i = 0; i < e.childNodes.length; i++) {
		e.childNodes[i].selected = e.childNodes[i].value == n ? 'selected' : '';
	}
	e = document.getElementById('text');
	e.focus();
	e.select();
}
</script>

<div class="mm white">
This quest <span class="blue">[<span class="yellow">1011</span>]</span> is called '<span class="yellow">Arachnophobia</span>',<br/>
for Adventurers levels <span class="yellow">180</span> to <span class="yellow">241</span>.<br />


<span class="hg"><a href="/npc/3438">Lord Vashir</a> [<a href="/area/61">The Towne of New Rigel</a>] is the master in charge of this quest.</span><br />

Spiders!  Arachnids!  I hate them!  No, I absolutely loathe them!  Not<br />
only do they creep around and sneak into places they don't belong, they can<br />
be quite vicious as well.  You are to seek out and destroy these loathsome<br />
pests.  Use whatever means you can come up with----smash them with a rock,<br />
smother them in a bag or just step on them.  I don't really care how you<br />
decide to deal with them, just kill them!  For your efforts on my behalf I<br />
will see that you are well rewarded if you cut their numbers down for me. <br />
Do hurry, as I want to sleep tonight without needing to be wary of these<br />
creatures sneaking into my bed.<br />

<span class="hy">Upon successful completion of this quest you can receive:</span><br />

<span class="hm">*</span>Up to <span class="yellow">80</span> quest points, <span class="yellow">8</span> practice points, <span class="yellow">28,000</span> experience points,<br/>
&nbsp;<span class="yellow">0</span> build points, <span class="yellow">0</span> piety, and <span class="yellow">7,500</span> gold pieces.<br />


You have <span class="yellow">300</span> minutes remaining to complete this quest.<br />

Arachnophobia consists of:<br />


	<div class="phase" id="phase1">


		<a class="hints" href="javascript:togPhase(1);">Phase 1</a>: Recover <a href="/item/1148">a shimmering scroll</a>. 		
